  [Text] The second Type-21 frigate, PNS [Pakistan Navy Ship] 
Babar, was inducted into the Pakistan Navy in Karachi today. 
Addressing the induction ceremony, Defense Minister Aftab Shahan 
Mirani, said development of the Navy, induction, and replace of 
ships, submarines, and aircraft is a continuing process. 
[sentence as heard] 
